    <entry>
      <title>温度场重建基准</title>
      <link href="/dataset/p/dataset2-index.html"/>
      <url>/dataset/p/dataset2-index.html</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>欢迎来到温度场重建数据集（Temperature Field Reconstruction Dataset，TFRD）主页。</p><h1 id="热源系统温度场重建任务"><a href="#热源系统温度场重建任务" class="headerlink" title="热源系统温度场重建任务"></a>热源系统温度场重建任务</h1><blockquote><p>温度场重建数据集面向电子设备热管理模块，解决由有限监测位置温度监控感兴趣位置（PoIs）温度，最终实现电子设备健康实时检测。</p></blockquote><h4 id="One-instance-one-task"><a href="#One-instance-one-task" class="headerlink" title="One instance one task"></a>One instance one task</h4><ul><li>基于点的建模<blockquote><p>学习点坐标到温度值的预测</p></blockquote></li></ul><p><img src="/dataset/images/figure/point.jpg" alt="point"></p><h4 id="One-family-one-task"><a href="#One-family-one-task" class="headerlink" title="One family one task"></a>One family one task</h4><ul><li>基于向量的建模<blockquote><p>学习监测点温度到PoIs温度映射</p></blockquote></li></ul><p><img src="/dataset/images/figure/vector.jpg" alt="vector"></p><ul><li>基于图像的建模<blockquote><p>学习监测点温度到PoIs温度映射（域离散化）</p></blockquote></li></ul><p><img src="/dataset/images/figure/image.jpg" alt="image"></p><ul><li>基于图关系的建模<blockquote><p>学习监测点温度到PoIs温度映射（构建graph关系）</p></blockquote></li></ul><p><img src="/dataset/images/figure/graph.jpg" alt="graph"></p><h1 id="引用"><a href="#引用" class="headerlink" title="引用"></a>引用</h1> <figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">@article&#123;gong_tfrd,</span><br><span class="line">    Author = &#123;Xiaoqian Chen and Zhiqiang Gong and Xiaoyu Zhao and Weien Zhou and Wen Yao&#125;,</span><br><span class="line">    Title = &#123;A Machine Learning Modelling Benchmark for Temperature Field Reconstruction of Heat-Source Systems&#125;,</span><br><span class="line">    Journal = &#123;arXiv preprint arXiv:2108.08298&#125;,</span><br><span class="line">    Year = &#123;2021&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125; </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">@article&#123;gong_pirl,</span><br><span class="line">    Author = &#123;Zhiqiang Gong and Weien Zhou and Jun Zhang and Wei Peng and Wen Yao&#125;,</span><br><span class="line">    Title = &#123;Physics-Informed Deep Reversible Regression Model for Temperature Field Reconstruction of Heat-Source Systems&#125;,</span><br><span class="line">    Journal = &#123;arXiv preprint arXiv:2106.11929&#125;,</span><br><span class="line">    Year = &#123;2021&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
      
