        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>欢迎来到热源布局预测数据集(Heat-Source Layout Dataset)主页。</p><h1 id="热源布局温度场预测任务"><a href="#热源布局温度场预测任务" class="headerlink" title="热源布局温度场预测任务"></a>热源布局温度场预测任务</h1><blockquote><p>热源布局温度场预测任务是对于给定热源组件布局以及边界条件，预测其整体温度场，为优化卫星舱内热源组件布局服务。</p></blockquote><div class="table-container"><table><thead><tr><th style="text-align:center"><img src="/dataset/images/layout.png" alt="upload successful"></th><th style="text-align:center"><img src="/dataset/images/boundary.png" alt="upload successful"></th><th style="text-align:center"><img src="/dataset/images/field.png" alt="upload successful"></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td style="text-align:center"><strong>热源布局模型</strong></td><td style="text-align:center"><strong>边界条件</strong></td><td style="text-align:center"><strong>温度场分布</strong></td></tr></tbody></table></div><h1 id="引用"><a href="#引用" class="headerlink" title="引用"></a>引用</h1><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">@article&#123;chen2021,</span><br><span class="line">    Author = &#123;Xianqi Chen and Xiaoyu Zhao and Zhiqiang Gong and Jun Zhang and Xiaoqian Chen and Wen Yao&#125;,</span><br><span class="line">    Title = &#123; A Deep Neural Network Surrogate Modeling Benchmark for Temperature Field Prediction of Heat Source Layout&#125;,</span><br><span class="line">    Journal = &#123;Science China-Physics, Mechanics &amp; Astronomy&#125;,</span><br><span class="line">    Year = &#123;2021&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125; </span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
      
